停用 開番好耐?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:53:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528360-20200526.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528360-20200526.htm&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHZUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=1f7bf488\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528360-20200526.htm&h=c648a117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528360-20200526.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n2020-05-26 HKT 10:30<br />\n<br />\n警方今早安排傳媒參觀新屋嶺扣留中心，說去年6月後考慮啟用中心，是由於被捕人士眾多，加上多間警署遭破壞及襲擊等因素，為盡快進行初步調查，去年8月至9月期間，新屋嶺扣留中心運作過4次，先後處理182人。<br />\n<br />\n警方說，被安排到新屋嶺的被捕人士，享有包括會見律師和親友等基本權利。警方當時派出了100至200名警員到新屋嶺參與案件調查及進行中心對內外溝通。<br />\n<br />\n警方說，新屋嶺扣留中心本身並無設有閉路電視，而為了加強內部保安、警員和被捕人士安全，去年10月加裝了8部閉路電視，當中5部是通往羈留室。"},{"pid":"e419931fe01bda29f2aa7d7fa6798faf43978157","tid":2124022,"uid":33522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:55:42.000Z","msg":"又指最近有6艘遠洋貨輪因有船員確診而需停泊在南丫島對出海面進行隔離檢疫，估計有人期間上岸時被島上居民發現報警。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要問清楚 班撚樣上岸播毒"},{"pid":"2348d798a48c450c6bc7291134b9f0d321320d38","tid":2124022,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:56:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d2863191f990fb09629704e60fd0dd93581c11","tid":2124022,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2348d798a48c450c6bc7291134b9f0d321320d38","tid":2124022,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:56:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgm